fields.name: Designer Order Placed
fields.email_body_template: Hello, /n You have a new order available.
fields.email_body_html_template:
Hello,

A new order {{ order.number }} is available.
Click here to view your order.

The order contains:

    {% for line in order.lines.all %}
  • {{ line.title }} - quantity: {{ line.quantity }}
    • {% endfor %}

fields.name: Designer Processing Order
fields.email_subject_template: Designer is Processing Your Order ({{ order.number }})
fields.email_body_template: Hello, /n The designer is currently processing your order.
fields.email_body_html_template:
Hello,

The designer: {{ shop_name }}
is currently processing your order {{ order.number }}.

The processed items are:

    {% for line in order.lines.all %}
  • {{ line.title }} - quantity: {{ line.quantity }}
    • {% endfor %}

fields.name: Order is in transit
fields.email_subject_template: Designer has Shipped Your Order ({{ order.number }})
fields.email_body_template: Hello, /n The designer has shipped your order and it is in transit.
fields.email_body_html_template:
Hello,

The designer: {{ shop_name }}
has shipped your order {{ order.number }}.

The shipped items are:

    {% for line in order.lines.all %}
  • {{ line.title }} - quantity: {{ line.quantity }}
    • {% endfor %}
